BREAKING: Four 'ISIS jihadis' arrested as police find TWENTY-FOUR suicide belts BREAKING: Four 'ISIS jihadis' arrested as police find TWENTY-FOUR suicide belts POLICE in Turkey claim they have arrested four members of ISIS and found 24 unexploded suicide belts. PUBLISHED: 11:39, Thu, Feb 9, 2017 | UPDATED: 11:50, Thu, Feb 9, 2017 GETTY Turkish armed forces arrest suspected jihadis
